  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Castle of Blackwater</strong> is a fast-paced<strong> </strong>social deduction game with a magical twist. Up to 10 strangers are trapped in a castle filled with danger, deception, and dark forces. Will you fight to survive and escape, or will you betray and eliminate?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Faction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Protectors </strong>–<strong> </strong>Complete tasks, form alliances, and expose the Satanic</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Satanic </strong>– Sabotage, eliminate, and manipulate your way to victory</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Forgotten </strong>– Play both sides and stir up chaos like a true wildcard</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Proximity Voice & Text Chat</strong> – Scream, scheme, or whisper sweet lies into your friends’ ears. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/1df6c11207ec730fa0a278b67970b986.poster.avif?t=1763131616\" width=800 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/1df6c11207ec730fa0a278b67970b986.webm?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/1df6c11207ec730fa0a278b67970b986.mp4?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 Unique Characters & Abilities –</strong> Silence players mid-discussion, transform into a werewolf, or literally read minds to uncover bloody secrets.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/fb482bc9b5f5af5fbb5aa041bbbd7267.poster.avif?t=1763131616\" width=800 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/fb482bc9b5f5af5fbb5aa041bbbd7267.webm?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/fb482bc9b5f5af5fbb5aa041bbbd7267.mp4?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>20+ Mini-Games & Tasks</strong> – Slice veggies like a ninja, chop down a tree like a lumberjack, or light candles like a medieval DJ in a musical memory game. <br>  <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/2fcad84ae3610b5e8012f50d46306950.poster.avif?t=1763131616\" width=800 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/2fcad84ae3610b5e8012f50d46306950.webm?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/2fcad84ae3610b5e8012f50d46306950.mp4?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>200+ Customisation Items </strong>- Equip awesome weapons, flashy shields, and fun emotes. Teabag enemies, dance with a skeleton, or go out in style with custom eliminations! <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/59ae9e39912166cd6856c5b724f460f3.poster.avif?t=1763131616\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/59ae9e39912166cd6856c5b724f460f3.webm?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/59ae9e39912166cd6856c5b724f460f3.mp4?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Death is not the end! </strong>– As a ghost, collect souls to buy power-ups for your team. Influence the game from beyond the grave! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/a000366587750614da1eb63d97e4468e.poster.avif?t=1763131616\" width=800 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/a000366587750614da1eb63d97e4468e.webm?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/a000366587750614da1eb63d97e4468e.mp4?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br>In the <strong>ever-lasting battle </strong>between good and evil, <strong>only one side will survive</strong> to claim the Castle’s victory.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Many members are joining our Discord to  keep up to date with  development. We're a small but active team, so if you have any suggestions or questions, we would love to talk to you on <strong>Discord.</strong></i>   <br>   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/cc86cf4e350748353e4e9274c9759b4e.avif?t=1763131616\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras_big/cc86cf4e350748353e4e9274c9759b4e.avif?t=1763131616 width=800 height=267 /></span></p>",
