atic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/59ae9e39912166cd6856c5b724f460f3.mp4?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Death is not the end! </strong>– As a ghost, collect souls to buy power-ups for your team. Influence the game from beyond the grave! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/a000366587750614da1eb63d97e4468e.poster.avif?t=1763131616\" width=800 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/a000366587750614da1eb63d97e4468e.webm?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/a000366587750614da1eb63d97e4468e.mp4?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br>In the <strong>ever-lasting battle </strong>between good and evil, <strong>only one side will survive</strong> to claim the Castle’s victory.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Many members are joining our Discord to  keep up to date with  development. We're a small but active team, so if you have any suggestions or questions, we would love to talk to you on <strong>Discord.</strong></i>   <br>   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/cc86cf4e350748353e4e9274c9759b4e.avif?t=1763131616\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras_big/cc86cf4e350748353e4e9274c9759b4e.avif?t=1763131616 width=800 height=267 /></span></p>",
